org.jhove2.module.format.tiff
Class TiffTag

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.module.format.tiff.TiffTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<TiffTag>
@Persistent
public class TiffTag
extends Object
implements Comparable<TiffTag>

Tiff Tags. Tags are initialized from a properties file in the form: Number:Type|Count|Default Value|Version for the tag number, type, cardinality, default value and TIFF version separated by the | character. Default Value and Version are not required however to indicate version an empty default value || must be defined. Example: 320:ColorMap|Short|3*2^BPS||5

Author:
mstrong
